Sentencas: A direct carbon fuel cell based on a conventional anode-supported tubular solid oxide fuel cell, which consisted of a NiO-YSZ anode support tube, a NiO-ScSZ anode functional layer, a ScSZ electrolyte film, and a LSM-ScSZ cathode, has been successfully achieved.
Titulo: A novel direct carbon fuel cell by approach of tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It used the carbon black as fuel and oxygen as the oxidant, and a preliminary examination of the DCFC has been carried out.
Titulo: A novel direct carbon fuel cell by approach of tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cell generated an acceptable performance with the maximum power densities of 104, 75, and 47 mW cm(-2) at 850, 800, and 750 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: A novel direct carbon fuel cell by approach of tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These results demonstrate the feasibility for carbon directly converting to electricity in tubular solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: A novel direct carbon fuel cell by approach of tubular solid oxide fuel cells
